=== Spec Example 8.5. Chomping Trailing Lines
--- from: http://www.yaml.org/spec/1.2/spec.html#id2795435
--- tags: spec literal scalar comment

--- in-yaml
 # Strip
  # Comments:
strip: |-
  # text
<SPC><SPC>
 # Clip
  # comments:

clip: |
  # text
<SPC>
 # Keep
  # comments:

keep: |+
  # text

 # Trail
  # comments.

--- in-json
{
  "strip": "# text",
  "clip": "# text\n",
  "keep": "# text\n\n"
}

--- out-yaml
strip: |-
  # text
clip: |
  # text
keep: |+
  # text

...

--- test-event
+STR
+DOC
+MAP
=VAL :strip
=VAL |# text
=VAL :clip
=VAL |# text\n
=VAL :keep
=VAL |# text\n\n
-MAP
-DOC
-STR
